rs, Tommy Steele \u2013 art direction\n*Jeffery Fey, George Mimnaugh \u2013 design\n*Andy Engel \u2013 logo design\n*Josh Kessler \u2013 photography\n\n==Charts and certifications==\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Weekly charts===\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n! Chart (1997)\n! Peak<br>position\n|-\n{{Album chart|Australia|5|artist=Foo Fighters|album=The Colour and the Shape|accessdate=26 June 2016}}\n|-\n{{Album chart|Austria|19|artist=Foo Fighters|album=The Colour and the Shape|accessdate=June 26, 2016}}\n|-\n{{Album chart|Flanders|7|artist=Foo Fighters|album=The Colour and the Shape|accessdate=June 26, 2016}}\n|-\n{{Album chart|Wallonia|18|artist=Foo Fighters|album=The Colour and the Shape|accessdate=June 26, 2016}}\n|-\n{{Album chart|Canada|8|chartid=3222|accessdate=October 20, 2019}}\n|-\n{{Album chart|Netherlands|39|artist=Foo Fighters|album=The Colour and the Shape|accessdate=June 26, 2016}}\n|-\n|[[European Top 100 Albums]] (''[[Music & Media]]'')<ref>{{cite magazine |date=May 31, 1997 |title=European Top 100 Albums |url=https://americanradiohistory.com/hd2/IDX-UK/Music/Archive-Music-Media-IDX/IDX/90s/97/MM-1997-05-31-OCR-Page-0020.pdf#search=%22european%20top%20100%20albums%20foo%20fighters%20colour%201997%22 |magazine=[[Music & Media]] |page=20|access-date=July 29, 2018}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|9\n|-\n{{Album chart|Finland|12|artist=Foo Fighters|album=The Colour and the Shape|accessdate=June 26, 2016}}\n|-\n{{Album chart|France|24|artist=Foo Fighters|album=The Colour and the Shape|accessdate=June 26, 2016}}\n|-\n{{Album chart|Germany|41|artist=Foo Fighters|album=The Colour and the Shape|accessdate=June 26, 2016}}\n|-\n|Greek Albums ([[IFPI Greece]])<ref>{{cite magazine |date=June 21, 1997 |title=Top National Sellers |url=https://americanradiohistory.com/hd2/IDX-UK/Music/Archive-Music-Media-IDX/IDX/90s/97/MM-1997-06-21-OCR-Page-0018.pdf#search=%22top%20national%20sellers%20foo%20fighters%20june%201997%22|magazine=[[Music & Media]] |page=20