ck (chart)|US<br />Main]]<br /><ref name=\"Allmusic singles\">{{cite web|url={{Allmusic|class=artist|id=foo-fighters-p144725/charts-awards/billboard-singles|pure_url=yes}} |title=Foo Fighters \u2013 Billboard Singles |accessdate=2008-05-08 |website=[[AllMusic]] }}</ref>\n!style=\"width:2em\"|[[ARIA Charts|AUS]]<br /><ref name=\"AUS chart1\">\n*For Top 50 positions: {{cite web| url=http://www.australian-charts.com/search.asp?search=Foo+fighters&cat=s |title=Discography Foo Fighters |publisher=[[Australian Recording Industry Association]] |accessdate=February 14, 2008}}\n*For \"My Hero\" and \"Walking After You\": {{cite book|last=Ryan|first=Gavin|title=Australia's Music Charts 1988\u20132010|year=2011|publisher=Moonlight Publishing|location=Mt. Martha, VIC, Australia}}</ref>\n!style=\"width:2em\"|[[Canadian Singles Chart|CAN]]<br><ref name=\"Canadian Top Singles positions\">{{cite magazine |url=http://www.collectionscanada.gc.ca/rpm/028020-110.01-e.php?PHPSESSID=c6btf3r8hs459qqt5ln3o3dcv5&q1=Foo+Fighters&q2=Top+Singles&interval=20 |title=Canadian Top Singles positions |magazine=[[RPM (magazine)|RPM]] |accessdate=2010-05-10 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121014085137/http://www.collectionscanada.gc.ca/rpm/028020-110.01-e.php?PHPSESSID=c6btf3r8hs459qqt5ln3o3dcv5&q1=Foo+Fighters&q2=Top+Singles&interval=20 |archivedate=2012-10-14 }}</ref><br>\n!style=\"width:2em\"|[[Canadian Rock/Alternative chart|CAN<br>Alt]]<br /><ref>{{cite magazine |url=http://www.collectionscanada.gc.ca/rpm/028020-110.01-e.php?PHPSESSID=c6btf3r8hs459qqt5ln3o3dcv5&q1=Foo+Fighters&q2=Rock%2FAlternative&interval=50 |title=Canadian Rock/Alternative positions |magazine=[[RPM (magazine)|RPM]] |accessdate=2010-05-05 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029204511/http://www.collectionscanada.gc.ca/rpm/028020-110.01-e.php?PHPSESSID=c6btf3r8hs459qqt5ln3o3dcv5&q1=Foo+Fighters&q2=Rock%2FAlternative&interval=50 |archivedate=2013-10-29 }}</ref>\n!style=\"width: