e news|title=Exclusive: Popular .338\u2032s In Handguns|url=https://americanhandgunner.com/exclusive-web-extra-popular-338s-in-handguns/|newspaper=American Handgunner|date=April 2012}}</ref>\n\nStarted by hunter and gun enthusiast [[J. D. Jones]], SSK Industries was begun to manufacture and market specific products related to hunting handguns<ref name=SSK_JDJones>{{cite web|title=About Page|url=http://sskindustries.com/about-ssk/|publisher=SSK Industries}}</ref> and ammunition. It has grown to a company that makes hundreds of different types of rounds.<ref name=sixguns>{{cite news|last=Fryxell|first=Glen E.|title=The Bullets of SSK|url=http://www.lasc.us/fryxellbulletsofssk.htm|accessdate=25 April 2014|newspaper=Sixguns.com}}</ref>\n\n==Notable Product==\nSSK has produced the largest center-fire [[rifle]] in history, the [[.950 JDJ]]. It is a .950 caliber which produces recoil equivalent to shooting ten .30-06 rifles at the same time.{{Citation needed|date=September 2018}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n[[Category:Ammunition designers]]\n[[Category:Firearm manufacturers of the United States]]\n\n\n{{firearms-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Biggus Saddus", "label": "safe", "comment": "Added SSK Firearms Website.", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/SSK_Industries"}
